  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">A right circular cone has a volume of <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one third, pi \"></span></span>&nbsp;cubic feet and a height of 9&nbsp;feet. What is the radius, in feet, of the base of the cone?</p>\n",
